<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَلَقَدْ رَوَى بِضْعٌ وَعِشْرُونَ امْرُوءٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مِنْ صَحْبِ أَحْمَدِ خَيْرَةِ الرَّحْمَنِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَخْبَارَ هَذَا الْبَابِ عَمَّنْ قَدْ أَتَى<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِالْوَحْيِ تَفْصِيلاً بِلا كِتْمَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَأَلَذُّ شَيْءٍ لِلْقُلُوبِ فَهِذِهِ الْـ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَخْبَارُ مَعَ أَمْثَالِهَا هِيَ بَهْجَةُ الإِيمَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَاللهِ لَوْلا رُؤْيَةُ الرَّحْمَنِ فِي الْـ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>جَنَّاتٍ مَا طَابَت لِذِي الْعِرْفَانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَعْلَى النَّعِيمِ نَعِيمُ رُؤْيَةِ وَجْهِهِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَخِطَابُه فِي جَنَّةِ الْحَيَوَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَأَشَدُّ شَيْءٍ فِي الْعَذَابِ حِجَابُهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>سُبْحَانَهُ عَنْ سَاكِنِي النِّيرَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَإِذَا رَآهُ الْمُؤْمِنُونَ نَسُوا الَّذِي<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>هُمْ فِيهِ مِمَّا نَالَتِ الْعَيْنَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَإِذَا تَوَارَى عَنْهُمْ عَادُوا إِلَى<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>لَذَّاتِهِمْ مِنْ سَائِرِ الأَلْوَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَلَهُمْ نَعِيمٌ عِنْدَ رُؤْيَتِهِ سِوَى<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>هَذَا النَّعِيمِ فَحَبَذَا الأَمْرَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَوَ مَا سَمِعْتَ سُؤَالَ أَعْرفِ خَلْقِهِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>بِجَلالِهِ الْمَبْعُوثِ بِالْقُرْآنِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>